//TEXT
<jaT0001>Ryota glared at the person who spoke up, furrowing his brow.
<enT0001>Ryota glared at the person who spoke up, furrowing his brow.

//TEXT
<jaT0002>Just as he thought, it was the one person on this station that he didn't want to see.
<enT0002>Just as he thought, it was the one person on this station that he didn't want to see.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0003>"Kazuhiko."
<enT0003>"Kazuhiko."

//TEXT 【Kazuhiko】
<jaT0004>"What a rude fellow, scowling as soon as you meet someone."
<enT0004>"What a rude fellow, scowling as soon as you meet someone."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0005>"I-I can't help it. I'm not a good enough actor to smile brightly when he sees an unpleasant face."
<enT0005>"I-I can't help it. I'm not a good enough actor to smile brightly when he sees an unpleasant face."

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0006>"Ryota-kun..."
<enT0006>"Ryota-kun..."

//TEXT
<jaT0007>Nao stood at his side with a worried look and poked Ryota on the back.
<enT0007>Nao stood at his side with a worried look and poked Ryota on the back.

//TEXT
<jaT0008>She was trying to signal that he shouldn't add fuel to the fire, but it didn't look like this would end that easily.
<enT0008>She was trying to signal that he shouldn't add fuel to the fire, but it didn't look like this would end that easily.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0009>"Don't stop me, Nao-san. That Kazuhiko always comes barging in like this. If you don't let him have it from time to time..."
<enT0009>"Don't stop me, Nao-san. That Kazuhiko always comes barging in like this. If you don't let him have it from time to time..."

//TEXT 【Kazuhiko】
<jaT0010>"Steadily ruder, aren't we. I have absolutely no interest in someone like you. Please stop acting like I'm following you around."
<enT0010>"Steadily ruder, aren't we. I have absolutely no interest in someone like you. Please stop acting like I'm following you around."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0011>"Wh-Why you. You've got some nerve saying that when you always appear out of nowhere just to be insulting."
<enT0011>"Wh-Why you. You've got some nerve saying that when you always appear out of nowhere just to be insulting."

//TEXT 【Kazuhiko】
<jaT0012>"Hmph. Oh, really? Isn't that just coincidence? Or maybe you're just too full of yourself?"
<enT0012>"Hmph. Oh, really? Isn't that just coincidence? Or maybe you're just too full of yourself?"

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0013>"Coincidence? Now see here, If the same thing happens four or five times a day, you don't call that 'coincidence'!"
<enT0013>"Coincidence? Now see here, If the same thing happens four or five times a day, you don't call that 'coincidence'!"

//TEXT
<jaT0014>Whenever they saw each other, they left such stinging remarks with each other.
<enT0014>Whenever they saw each other, they left such stinging remarks with each other.

//TEXT
<jaT0015>They weren't stalking each other, but it was too often for the gentle, timid, indecisive Ryota to put up with.
<enT0015>They weren't stalking each other, but it was too often for the gentle, timid, indecisive Ryota to put up with.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0016>"First of all, why did you choose this training facility, Kazuhiko? What about your usual followers?"
<enT0016>"First of all, why did you choose this training facility, Kazuhiko? What about your usual followers?"

//TEXT 【Kazuhiko】
<jaT0017>"It isn't a mystery or anything. Didn't you hear the instructors say 'one should strive to do things on one's own'?"
<enT0017>"It isn't a mystery or anything. Didn't you hear the instructors say 'one should strive to do things on one's own'?"

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0018>"You're not one to follow decision like that though, are you?"
<enT0018>"You're not one to follow decision like that though, are you?"

//TEXT
<jaT0019>Ryota's comeback was good. Kazuhiko was the heir to a prominent domestic enterprise. He was even allowed to wear a custom-made uniform, so it would be strange for him to abide by a rule that others didn't.
<enT0019>Ryota's comeback was good. Kazuhiko was the heir to a prominent domestic enterprise. He was even allowed to wear a custom-made uniform, so it would be strange for him to abide by a rule that others didn't.

//TEXT
<jaT0020>In truth, the semi-aristocratic group he associated with all take separate courses together.
<enT0020>In truth, the semi-aristocratic group he associated with all take separate courses together.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0021>"Knowing you, perhaps there's a woman you're after on the Aries? That's probably the reason. That's why you had them accept your sudden transfer to the Aries."
<enT0021>"Knowing you, perhaps there's a woman you're after on the Aries? That's probably the reason. That's why you had them accept your sudden transfer to the Aries."

//TEXT 【Kazuhiko】
<jaT0022>"Hmph. That may be what you would do, but stop prying into other people's business. You're just jumping to conclusions."
<enT0022>"Hmph. That may be what you would do, but stop prying into other people's business. You're just jumping to conclusions."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0023>"I-I-I-I am not some kind of good-for-nothing!"
<enT0023>"I-I-I-I am not some kind of good-for-nothing!"

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0024>"Calm down you two..."
<enT0024>"Calm down you two..."

//TEXT
<jaT0025>Nao quickly held Ryota back as he tried to step forward. Then to smooth things over, she presented the pink paper bag she was carrying.
<enT0025>Nao quickly held Ryota back as he tried to step forward. Then to smooth things over, she presented the pink paper bag she was carrying.

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0026>"Come now, don't fight. Why don't we have some tea together? My mother sent some delicious cookies."
<enT0026>"Come now, don't fight. Why don't we have some tea together? My mother sent some delicious cookies."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0027>"......"
<enT0027>"......"

//TEXT 【Kazuhiko】
<jaT0028>"......"
<enT0028>"......"

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0029>"Sheesh, don't ignore each other."
<enT0029>"Sheesh, don't ignore each other."

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0030>"Let's all get along. We're stuck together on this small space station until we return to Earth, aren't we?"
<enT0030>"Let's all get along. We're stuck together on this small space station until we return to Earth, aren't we?"

//TEXT 【Kazuhiko】
<jaT0031>"I had no intention of getting involved in some quarrel. Yet this one made such trifling remarks..."
<enT0031>"I had no intention of getting involved in some quarrel. Yet this one made such trifling remarks..."

//TEXT
<jaT0032>Kazuhiko said, pointing at Ryota.
<enT0032>Kazuhiko said, pointing at Ryota.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0033>"You know, don't you think that's a blatant lie?"
<enT0033>"You know, don't you think that's a blatant lie?"

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0034>"Ryota-kun, calm down, calm down. Here, I'll go get us some drinks. Are the two of you alright with black tea?"
<enT0034>"Ryota-kun, calm down, calm down. Here, I'll go get us some drinks. Are the two of you alright with black tea?"

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0035>"......"
<enT0035>"......"

//TEXT 【Kazuhiko】
<jaT0036>"......"
<enT0036>"......"

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0037>"Ei!"
<enT0037>"Ei!"

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0038>"Ow! What was that for, Nao-san?"
<enT0038>"Ow! What was that for, Nao-san?"

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0039>"At least give a reply. Is black tea alright with you?"
<enT0039>"At least give a reply. Is black tea alright with you?"

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0040>"Yes..."
<enT0040>"Yes..."

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0041>"Alright, then wait here."
<enT0041>"Alright, then wait here."

//TEXT
<jaT0042>After the two of them reluctantly nodded in agreement, Nao jogged over to the counter.
<enT0042>After the two of them reluctantly nodded in agreement, Nao jogged over to the counter.

//TEXT
<jaT0043>Then she placed her order with the man at the counter and shortly thereafter, she came back carrying a tray with three cups spread on it.
<enT0043>Then she placed her order with the man at the counter and shortly thereafter, she came back carrying a tray with three cups spread on it.

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0044>"Sorry for the wait."
<enT0044>"Sorry for the wait."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0045>"......"
<enT0045>"......"

//TEXT 【Kazuhiko】
<jaT0046>"......"
<enT0046>"......"

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0047>"Eh? Huh? Don't tell me neither of you uttered a single word while you waited?"
<enT0047>"Eh? Huh? Don't tell me neither of you uttered a single word while you waited?"

//TEXT
<jaT0048>......
<enT0048>......

//TEXT
<jaT0049>A long, long moment of silence went by.
<enT0049>A long, long moment of silence went by.

//TEXT
<jaT0050>This long silence eloquently expressed the situation that had continued in Nao's absence.
<enT0050>This long silence eloquently expressed the situation that had continued in Nao's absence.

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0051>"Th-that's no good. That's not what I..."
<enT0051>"Th-that's no good. That's not what I..."

